cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IOT, cs.DS, cs.SE 

The paper discusses privacy concerns in the context of IoT and proposes a privacy-preserving machine learning approach. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses machine learning approaches, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The paper specifically focuses on IoT, which makes cs.IOT (Internet of Things) a likely category. The paper also involves data processing and classification, which makes cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible category. Finally, the paper proposes a new approach, which involves running a lightweight neural network at IoT objects and a deep neural network in the cloud, which makes cs.SE (Software Engineering) a possible category as well.
